SUMMARY:Electronic Evidence in Criminal Investigations
DESCRIPTION:Join the Criminal Law Society in hosting former U.S. Attorney
  for the Southern District of Indiana Zachary Myers and former Task Force
  Officer Darin Odier (along with his Electronic Scent Detection K-9\, Hun
 ter). Myers will discuss the legal nuances of electronic evidence\, and O
 dier and Hunter will discuss and demonstrate their role in the detection 
 and seizure of electronic evidence in criminal investigations.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join the Criminal Law Society in hostin
 g former U.S. Attorney for the Southern District of Indiana Zachary Myers
  and former Task Force Officer Darin Odier (along with his Electronic Sce
 nt Detection K-9\, Hunter). Myers will discuss the legal nuances of elect
 ronic evidence\, and Odier and Hunter will discuss and demonstrate their 
 role in the detection and seizure of electronic evidence in criminal inve
 stigations.&#160\;</p>
