SUMMARY:Advocating for Justice: Protecting the Rights of Individuals with
  Disabilities
DESCRIPTION:Description for publicity:  Join the Family &amp\; Disability
  Law Association for a special guest speaker event featuring Melissa Keye
 s\, the Executive Director of Indiana Disability Rights. Indiana Disabili
 ty Rights works to protect and promote the legal and civil rights of indi
 viduals with disabilities across the State of Indiana.  This event offers
  a valuable opportunity for students interested in disability law\, publi
 c interest advocacy\, civil rights\, and government service to hear direc
 tly from a leader working on the front lines of protecting the rights of 
 individuals with disabilities.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Description for publicity:<br />  Join 
 the Family &amp\; Disability Law Association for a special guest speaker 
 event featuring Melissa Keyes\, the Executive Director of Indiana Disabil
 ity Rights. Indiana Disability Rights works to protect and promote the le
 gal and civil rights of individuals with disabilities across the State of
  Indiana.</p><p>  This event offers a valuable opportunity for students i
 nterested in disability law\, public interest advocacy\, civil rights\, a
 nd government service to hear directly from a leader working on the front
  lines of protecting the rights of individuals with disabilities.&#160\;<
 /p>
