SUMMARY:CCD Seminar Series with Professor Solomon N. Abesha
DESCRIPTION:Prof. Solomon N. Abesha is an associate professor and former 
 dean of the College of Law and Governance Studies at Addis Ababa Universi
 ty. He earned his PhD from Utrecht University\, Netherlands\; his LLM fro
 m Amsterdam University\, Netherlands\; and his LLB from Addis Ababa Unive
 rsity\, Ethiopia. His research focuses on comparative constitutional fede
 ralism\, law and development\, and human rights.  All are invited to atte
 nd Prof. Abesha's talk at the CCD (618 E 3rd St).&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Prof. Solomon N. Abesha is an associate
  professor and former dean of the College of Law and Governance Studies a
 t Addis Ababa University. He earned his PhD from Utrecht University\, Net
 herlands\; his LLM from Amsterdam University\, Netherlands\; and his LLB 
 from Addis Ababa University\, Ethiopia. His research focuses on comparati
 ve constitutional federalism\, law and development\, and human rights.</p
 ><p>  All are invited to attend Prof. Abesha's talk at the CCD (618 E 3rd
  St).&#160\;</p>
