SUMMARY:ILAP Spring Training: What Makes a Prison: Construction and Desig
 n of Correctional Facilities in Indiana
DESCRIPTION:"The suffering of the convicted is carefully arranged to take
  place somewhere out of sight." - Robert A. Ferguson\, Inferno: An Anatom
 y of American Punishment.What happens when prison conditions go from unpl
 easant to inhumane? How can incarcerated people have their rights vindica
 ted? How are these issues manifesting in Indiana?Join us for a thoughtful
  overview on the intricacies of prison politics and the practical reality
  of navigating these challenges in Indiana.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt\; font-fam
 ily: 'Arial'\,sans-serif\; color: black\;">"The suffering of the convicte
 d is carefully arranged to take place somewhere out of sight." - Robert A
 . Ferguson\, Inferno: An Anatomy of American Punishment.</span></p><p><sp
 an style="font-size: 10.0pt\; font-family: 'Arial'\,sans-serif\; color: b
 lack\;">What happens when prison conditions go from unpleasant to inhuman
 e? How can incarcerated people have their rights vindicated? How are thes
 e issues manifesting in Indiana?</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 10.
 0pt\; font-family: 'Arial'\,sans-serif\; color: black\;">Join us for a th
 oughtful overview on the intricacies of prison politics and the practical
  reality of navigating these challenges in Indiana.</span></p>
